{"tid":1415251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再比同溫層蒙蔽","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:32:10.000Z","uid":139484,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9ddca029377de69198eee7d12a00358e471b93a3","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"今日柒婆已經話會日日搵狗開記招<br />\n代表我哋要打嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輿論戰強度唔係以前個level</span></span><br />\n政府已經摩拳擦掌 喺示威者武力升級嘅時候全力開動文宣機器<br />\n想將市民同勇武分割 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將社會混亂歸咎喺示威者身上</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算連登上面講 出核彈都唔割<br />\n我哋都要做最壞打算 就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可能真係會有市民動搖</span></span><br />\n依家政府就係想令一般人淡忘 慢慢搶返個道德高地 瓦解成個運動<br />\n<br />\n就算經歷左七一之後民意冇逆轉<br />\n我哋都唔可以掉以輕心<br />\n最近有兩個好危險嘅訊號<br />\n第一個係搞狗宿舍嗰陣波及消防<br />\n竟然大部分連登仔都諗住「鬼叫佢同黑警做鄰居」<br />\n<br />\n第二個就係有人影相嗰陣 已經好容易trigger到衝突<br />\n唔似以前咁克制 叫返自己人戴口罩 叫人唔好影相就算<br />\n<br />\n連登本身係一個好大嘅同溫層<br />\n不過政府文宣機器target嘅正正就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會上連登嘅人</span></span><br />\n就算連登入面唔割席 唔代表連登出面民意唔會炒車<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">建議手足每次行動都可以有一隊和理非負責pr<br />\n可以整連儂牆解釋返個行動<br />\n同埋喺行動入面緩和手足同普通市民嘅情緒<br />\n不過要拿捏好分數 唔好左膠上身伏左手足<br />\n<br />\n仲有旗手真係好重要 唔單只係比自己人睇 更加係比鏡頭睇 班狗點樣喺冇衝擊嘅情況下突襲 狙擊示威者 甚至路過市民<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1c9a7e2dec5e8543609c831fe5994f27746641aa","tid":1415251,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f6f24b101a1a7d116416fac7a367d524038849","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6041c61a87659b6a3e9b286a7f04c2275d4292d","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af597037973398773cebca1b52cccab954b9ae11","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc30565684634198189c4f229bdb610fe6620ed","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d7a643f2c60b8e90445a49454e7b4d0385856b","tid":1415251,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"4134a5220c3ad34cfea2b78bb549d89f325160c5","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"推到十點"},{"pid":"cd000eabe1caa7226ee2fbad0c887c580e4616a7","tid":1415251,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"E個真，推"},{"pid":"9ee660089f2cd2f1118934194313a0d7c37918c2","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196b567d533515094cb79e5a6c89bbf07e1e857f","tid":1415251,"ui