r: red;\">不過唔好左膠到好似社工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7f446b364f2547193861a2bcb9697fc4b714a57","tid":1415251,"uid":139484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a8bfd97d87dcd61e3a9274172b4329b92afdceb","tid":1415251,"uid":43842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"呢個真 要解釋返成個行動<br />\n好多人睇唔到前因後果就覺得示威者暴力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"示威者記者會係一個好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足終於有意識要反制文宣機器"}]}